test.name: Compare HTML Table With Parquet Data

kw.name: Open Browser
kw.msg: Opening browser 'Chrome' to base url 'file://tafordqe\Robot Framework result/report.html'.
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to the optional ``url``.

kw.name: Get WebElement
kw.doc: Returns the first WebElement matching the given ``locator``.

kw.name: Table Read Data
kw.msg: ${df_html} = Facility Type Visit Date Average Time Spent 0 Hospital 2025-09-02 41.33 1 Clinic 2025-09-02 49 2 Hospital 2025-09-01 ...
kw.doc: Reads a table web element and returns a pandas DataFrame keyed by column header.

kw.name: Read Parquet Data
kw.msg: ${df_parquet} = facility_type visit_date avg_time_spent 24607 Hospital 2025-08-27 20.50 24626 Specialty Center 2025-08-28 31.33 24631 Hospital 2025-08-30 31...
kw.doc: Reads partitioned parquet dataset from a folder. Automatically detects subfolder partitions. Optionally filters by visit_date.

kw.name: Compare Dataframes
kw.doc: Compare DataFrames by values. Returns (match_bool, differences_as_string)

kw.name: Run Keyword If
kw.doc: Runs the given keyword with the given arguments, if ``condition`` is true.

test.doc: Open HTML file, read table, read parquet data, and compare.
